students who fractured their legs when they jumped from 
secondstory windows in their dormitories at dhaka university news 
reports said 
a tremor with a richter scale reading of 63 rocked parts of 
pakistan and nepal saturday officials reported its epicenter was 
in the hindu kush mountains of afghanistan and northern pakistan 
the openended richter scale is a gauge of energy released by an 
earthquake as measured by ground movement recorded on a 
seismograph 
a quake with a magnitude of 5 can cause considerable damage one 
of 6 can cause severe damage and one of 7 is capable of 
widespread heavy damage 
 
